l'année dernière à marienbad ( released in the us as last year at marienbad and in the uk as last year in marienbad ) is a 1961 french-italian film directed by alain resnais from a screenplay by alain robbe-grillet .   the film is famous for its enigmatic narrative structure , in which truth and fiction are difficult to distinguish , and the temporal and spatial relationship of the events is open to question .   its dreamlike nature has both fascinated and baffled viewers ; many have hailed the work as a masterpiece , while others consider it incomprehensible .